                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\">\n                <placeName>Charleston</placeName>\n                <date>Dec 25/59</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Reverd. S Morais</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <placeName>Cherry St. Synagogue Phila.</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dr Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\"><persName>Mr. Abraham Harris</persName> of your city having\n                made<lb/> application to our congregation for the situation of minister we have<lb/>\n                invited him here on a probationary visit. Since his arrival various<lb/> rumors have\n                sprung up prejudicial to his character as a man a<lb/> minister or an Israelite, on\n                being informed of them <persName>Mr. H</persName> very properly<lb/> declined\n                officiating until an oppy. was afforded for thorough investiga<lb/>=tion, he has\n                given your address with that of several other gentlemen<lb/> with whom he is bid\n                acquainted, he stands before us quite a stran<lb/>=ger. Our object now is to do\n                justice to the congregation as well as to <persName>Mr. H</persName><lb/> would\n                therefore solicit your information on the following points<lb/> which shall be held\n                confidential if you so desire it.</p>\n            <p>Amongst other things he is charged with having preached or lec=<lb/>=tured in a\n                    <sic>christian</sic> pulpit or lecture room to Christian audiences<lb/> That he\n                made application to the <sic>Babtists</sic> or some other Chrisn. denomi<lb/>=nation\n                to take orders for missionary purposes to the south, there are<lb/> other rumors of\n                minor importance which I will not trouble you with but<lb/> request you to give such\n                information as you possess of <persName>Mr. Hs</persName> standing<lb/> and\n                character and of his qualifications for such appointment.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Your attention and early reply will be highly appreciated<lb/> by\n                our congregation as well as by</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Yours very respectfully</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\"><persName role=\"author\">Joshua Lazarus</persName> Chairman</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Conc. of investigation</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p32z1389t/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
